data.description: This long time family home has great original craftsman wood work. Beautiful fireplace and dining room with a builtin buffet boasting original glass. All rooms are huge from the living room, dining room and master bedroom. The large galley kitchen is bright and has two cozy rooms adjoining, one for a sitting area and a charming breakfast nook. Lovely graceful stairway leads to the upstairs landing and 3 huge bedrooms. Owners believe there are hardwoods under all carpets. Oversized two car garage.
